OL,3,CMan jailed after installing cameras
OL,4,Cand secretly filming people in their
OL,5,Chomes
OL,7,FAn electrician, who spent more than
OL,8,Ften years secretly recording people in
OL,9,Ftheir own homes, has pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fvoyeurism.
OL,12,FJames Denholm, 34, previously pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to multiple charges including
OL,14,Fvoyeurism and stalking in a hearing at
OL,15,FAberdeen Sheriff's Court.
OL,17,FHe was caught after a victim found a
OL,18,Frecording device under her bed on May
OL,19,F23, 2022 and called police,
OL,20,Fprosecutors said.
