OL,7,FA search was carried out at Denholm's
OL,8,FAberdeen home where officers
OL,9,Fdiscovered various hard drives, SD
OL,10,Fcards, mobile phones, laptops and
OL,11,Fcameras.
OL,13,FEvidence of his offending, involving
OL,14,F17 people, was recovered from the
OL,15,Fdevices, with videos dating from June
OL,16,F2013 until August 2023.
OL,18,FA number of women were filmed in
OL,19,Fintimate situations without their
OL,20,Fconsent, prosecutors said.
