OL,7,FThe 34-year-old also admitted
OL,8,Fpossessing indecent images and videos
OL,9,Fof children between 2007 and 2012.
OL,11,FHe pleaded guilty to the offences on
OL,12,FJuly 22 and was jailed for two years
OL,13,Fand eight months when he appeared at
OL,14,FAberdeen Sheriff Court for sentencing
OL,15,Fon Monday September 2, the Crown
OL,16,FOffice said.
OL,18,FAlison McKenzie, procurator fiscal for
OL,19,FGrampian, Highlands and Islands,
OL,20,Fdescribed Denholm's behaviour as
OL,21,F"depraved".
